songs.title: Coraline
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics of Snippet

[Intro]
Ahh-ah-huh (ey)
Ahh-ah (ey-yeah)
That's Scheme who killed it!
Ahh-ah-ah (ey)
Ahh

[Hook]
I ain't wasting time (ah-huh)
She from the other side, call her Coraline, ah (ah-huh)
The demon's on a ride, she's coming after my life, ah
Something in here ain't right, no
She gave me a few pills (ah)
Some blue and some white, ah

[Verse]
Life is a bitch and my struggles are mood swings
Other people may say that my life is a movie
